{"questionId":"21095","questionHtml":"<p>Find the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math> and the value of <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi></math>.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><strong>METHOD 1</strong></p>\n<p>recognition that blade length = amplitude,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mtext>max</mtext><mo>-</mo><mtext>min</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>91</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>centre of windmill = vertical shift,&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><mtext>max</mtext><mo>+</mo><mtext>min</mtext></mrow><mn>2</mn></mfrac></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>8</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>21</mn></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>A1</strong></em></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>METHOD 2</strong></p>\n<p>attempting to form two equations in terms of &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>q</mi></math>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<em><strong>&nbsp;(M1)(M1)</strong></em></p>\n<p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>12</mn><mo>.</mo><mn>1192</mn><mo>…</mo><mo>=</mo><mi>p</mi><mo> </mo><mi>cos</mi><mfenced><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">π</mi></mrow><mn>10</mn></mfrac><mo>·</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mfenc